    "pageContentHtml": "<p>PreClass Work is reading Bengston and Keshav and taking a first look (what Bengston calls &quot;survey&quot; and &quot;query&quot;) Amodei, et al.  There are also some flashcards for &quot;memorizing&quot; Amodei&#39;s five concrete problems.</p>\n<p>In class, we will talk about the two techniques and apply them to the paper together. NOTE: deck now includes my slides from BI orientation - they need to be thinned out.</p>\n<p>Assignment One (in PostClass Work): Analogize each of five problems to familiar context and then rewrite the final conclusion paragraph of Amodei et al. paper.</p>\n",
